  <Summary>The Invisible Melman!: ALF becomes temporarily invisible after ingesting a sponge.

Love Is in the Hair!: ALF gives Brian advice on how to get Laura to notice him.

One Melmillion Years B.C.: ALF tells Kate a tale about his earliest ancestor, Gog Shumway.

Truth Is Stranger Than Friction!: ALF uses a Melmacian wax to clean the Tanner's floor.

Past Performance!: ALF follows Lucky (the Tanner's cat) through a time portal into the past.

Lost at Sea-Biscuit!: 
ALF accompanies Willie on a sailboat trip.

</Summary>
